## Audio backfill resume (if any items remain)

If `turn_audio` count is below the total turn count after this run, audio gen can be resumed at any time:

```bash
cd /Users/dr.ali/projects/fluentia-lms
export SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN=<token>
export PROD_SR=<from `curl /v1/projects/<ref>/api-keys`>
export ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=$(grep '^ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=' .env | cut -d= -f2)
export HARD_CAP_CHARS=750000
node scripts/retention/generate-audio.cjs
```
Fully idempotent — checks Supabase Storage object existence before each API call. Re-run as many times as needed.

